|7 |      └─HASH JOIN              |                      |1198    |2217        |
|8 |        ├─TABLE FULL SCAN      |customer_address      |500     |24          |
|9 |        └─HASH JOIN            |                      |1250    |1944        |
|10|          ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |store                 |12      |3           |
|11|          └─HASH JOIN          |                      |1311    |1791        |
|12|            ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |date_dim              |200     |57          |
|13|            └─HASH JOIN        |                      |2407    |1441        |
|14|              ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|household_demographics|200     |28          |
|15|              └─TABLE FULL SCAN|store_sales           |5000    |870         |
=================================================================================
